title: Celebrity Gossip Part 1 - Red Solo Cups In Australia
description: Margot Robbie had to smuggle a suitcase filled with something they don’t have in Australia because her friends think it’s iconic. And Katy Perry explains why she doesn’t have a full time nanny for her 2 year old… even though she could really use a full time nanny.
